{"type":"message","id":"c9f8d6a1","parentId":"a28ca034","timestamp":"2026-03-19T06:15:20.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context usage is at 68%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. The system is alerting me to consider starting a new session. Let me check the session status to see the current token usage and understand the situation better.\n\nThe user hasn't asked me anything specific here - this is just a context monitor alert. According to AGENTS.md, I should stay quiet instead of creating vague or noisy proactivity. Since there's no specific action requested and the context is still at 68% (not critical yet), I should just acknowledge this and wait for user input.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - this is a cron job that runs the context monitor. The system is telling me context is at 68%. The alert says \"Consider starting a new session to reset context\" but I shouldn't just automatically create a new session without user consent for the main session.\n\nLet me check if there's a HEARTBEAT.md or any specific instructions about what to do in this case.","thinkingSignature":"e553a997cf9e0f60a3501a435e784993dfbbcc9159e311d80ca6395e4e4dfe1b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jhdjcn2vdc9j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":395,"output":238,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37635,"cost":{"input":0.0001185,"output":0.0002856,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00151416}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773900913458}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c61b050","parentId":"c9f8d6a1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T06:15:20.257Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jhdjcn2vdc9j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Context Manager Check\n\n- Run session_status to check current context usage\n- If context > 60%, consider saving memory and preparing for session switch\n- Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n- Update ~/proactivity/memory/working-buffer.md if needed\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read ./skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md\n- Use ~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside ~/self-improving/ changed since the last reviewed change, return HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n## Proactivity Check\n\n- Read ~/proactivity/heartbeat.md\n- Re-check active blockers, promised follow-ups, stale work, and missing decisions\n- Ask what useful check-in or next move would help right now\n- Message the user only when something changed or needs a decision\n- Update ~/proactivity/session-state.md after meaningful follow-through\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773900920255}}
{"type":"message","id":"dcd0b775","parentId":"2c61b050","timestamp":"2026-03-19T06:15:26.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HEARTBEAT.md tells me to:\n1. Check session_status for context usage\n2. Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n\nThe context is at 68%, which is above the 60% threshold. Let me check the session state and proactivity memory to see if there are any active tasks that need to be preserved before a potential session switch.\n\nActually, the user hasn't asked me to do anything. This is just a monitoring cron job. The context is at 68%, which is high but not critical. I should check if there are any active tasks that would be affected by a session switch, and if so, I might want to inform the user. But if there are no urgent matters, I should just stay quiet and let them know when they ask me something.\n\nLet me check the proactivity session state.","thinkingSignature":"18266b4473b03cb1f03c3f37939c45014e2ee405fe65d7e2b3311fe9698191ab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3teijd0nxt0v_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\proactivity\\session-state.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":878,"output":211,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38091,"cost":{"input":0.0002634,"output":0.0002532,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016266599999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773900920257}}
